{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_09_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 二人の関係",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "home-office-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Moon Tempest became part of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2100,
          "startTime": 2.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "は～、やっと戻って来れた～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew~ I'm finally back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6000001352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にレッスン、午後は月スト五人でインタビュー\nそれから次のライブの打ち合わせをして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lessons in the morning‚ an interview with all Moon Tempest members\nin the afternoon‚ a meeting for the next live show‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "最後は読書系動画配信者のチャンネルにゲスト出演……\n凄く濃い一日でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and finally‚ we made a guest appearance on a book-loving video streamer's channel…\nIt was a really packed day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってから、月ストだけじゃなくて\nメンバーそれぞれのソロの仕事も格段に増えたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After becoming BIG4‚ not just Moon Tempest‚ but\neach member's solo work has increased dramatically.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛小説が好き……という話をあちこちでするように\nなってから、関係するお仕事が多くなった気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I started talking about how I like romance novels here and there‚\nI feel like I've been getting a lot more work related to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "まさかお仕事に繋がるとは思ってなかったんですけど\n世界が広がった感じがしてとっても嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought it would lead to work‚ but\nI'm really happy because I feel like my world has expanded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6573858341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったよ\n少しでも無理があったらいつでも言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's good to hear.\nIf you ever feel like you're pushing yourself too hard‚ let me know anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "この後は、今度のお仕事についての軽い打ち合わせ\nですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After this‚ we have a brief meeting about our next job‚\nright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666650136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9066.659545899995,
          "startTime": 67.1333245595
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。今度出演する予定の歌番組についてなんだが\nトークコーナーでこんなことを話してほしいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. It's about the music program you're appearing on this time‚\nthey want you to talk about these topics in the talk corner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1333316803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "「月ストとして、そしてメンバー五人それぞれの\n今後の目標」……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Future goals as Moon Tempest‚ and as each of\nthe five members\"… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5666721344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になって、今まで以上に忙しくなって……\nみんなの考え方も変化してるかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that we're BIG4‚ we're busier than ever before…\nEveryone's way of thinking might be changing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7666650136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "今のみんながどんな目標を話すのか、気になります\nでもまずは、私の考えをまとめないとですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what kind of goals everyone will talk about now.\nBut first‚ I need to organize my own thoughts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5666629791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A Few Days Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3333296458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4000019073
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4000019073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～。大好きな小説家さんと対談するなんて初めてで\n心臓が口から飛び出そうでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew. It was my first time having a dialogue with a novelist I admire much‚\nI thought my heart was going to leap out of my mouth……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7333296458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1666692814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "けど、イメトレしたおかげでうまくやれて良かったです\nこの後はラジオ局で収録ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I'm glad I was able to do well thanks to the image training.\nAfter this‚ we have a recording at the radio station‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5999987284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。五分後にタクシーが到着する予定だから\nそれに乗って向かおう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. The taxi is scheduled to arrive in five minutes‚\nso let's hop in and head over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.866665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今度の歌番組で話す目標は思いついたか？\n……って、その表情……だいぶ悩んでいるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ have you decided on the goals you'll talk about on the music show?\n……Or rather‚ that expression… looks like you're having a lot of trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.966665395,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11499.966666700004,
          "startTime": 138.4666320617
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0999980371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ちょっと、というかかなり悩んでて\nこれ、見てもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… A little‚ or rather‚ I'm having a lot of trouble.\nCould you take a look at this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2333320617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.665975399991,
          "startTime": 141.1999980371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.1999980371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "これは……メモ？　凄いな、びっしり書かれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… a memo? Wow‚ it's densely written.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1999980371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "今までいろんなことがあったから、その時々で\nどんなことを考えていたのか書き出してみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot has happened until now‚ so I tried\nwriting down my thoughts for each moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7999885558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.899981761
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、なんていうか言葉が溢れ過ぎて……\n全然まとまらないんですよ～！　う～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ somehow‚ I have too much to say…\nI can't organize them at all~! Ugh~~……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.9333218891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.3666484277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになった頃は\n琴乃ちゃんを支えることだけ考えてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I became an idol‚\nI was only thinking about supporting Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.3666552225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、四人になった時に「月ストを支えるんだ」って\n決めて……今では私自身が輝きたいとも思ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ when we became a quartet‚ I decided \"I have to support\nMoon Tempest‚\" and now… I also want to shine on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.6999987284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.1333150943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。それなら、今話したことを目標として\n話せばいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. In that case‚ why don't you talk about\nwhat you just said as your goal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.9999987284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.8666484277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうなんですけど、今でも変わらず琴乃ちゃんの\nことを大事に思ってる気持ちも、もちろんあるんです",
      "translations": {
